{
  "stem": "14002.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like they build it-- as a matter of fact, they built the crematorium night-- right near the kitchen, not far from the kitchen, right there in that camp.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anyway, when it came-- I think it was-- it was a very bad winter.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They used to-- we had to take a shower every-- every two weeks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We had to go naked, in the winter, from the barrack, to go to the shower [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and back, also.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It doesn't make any difference how deep the snow was or how cold it was.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And by God-- and for God's name, nobody ever got a cold there from that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I think it was in-- in March, by the end of-- by the end-- by the end of February.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The-- the-- probably the Allies found out, for some reason or another, where the-- where that factory is.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Where that factory is.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They started to bomb that mountain, day and night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we didn't go to work no more there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One day, by the end of February, they took us, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they took us on a march.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't know to what city it was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it was near the Danube.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For a couple days, they took us on a march there, till we came to the river Danube.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Down there, was a-- was a-- a boat waiting for us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In that boat, there was tar.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That boat, it-- it- it was transporting tar.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we had to make-- we had to push ourselves in that boat, on top of that tar, whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they took us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Where, we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
